description: FinCanna Capital Corp. operates as an investment company for the licensed cannabis industry in the United States. It provides financing for companies operating in the cannabis sector. The company has royalty agreements with Green Compliance Inc.; and Refined Resin. FinCanna Capital Corp. was incorporated in 2016 is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Vern  Vipul B.A., LL.B., M. Tax
